meta.commit_message: ⚡ Tidy superconductors 3 \(#3666\) CITATION.cff CMakeLists.txt CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md CONTRIBUTING.md LICENSE.txt README.md cmake documentation examples mkdocs.yml process process-tracking-data process.egg-info requirements.txt requirements_dev.txt ruff.toml scripts setup.py source tests tracking valgrind-python.supp Add EUTF4 Nb3Sn critical current density analysis and visualization - Introduced a new image file for the critical current density surface of EUTF4 Nb3Sn at zero strain. - Updated the superconductors documentation to include parameters and critical surface for EUTF4 Nb3Sn. - Added a new Python script for plotting the critical current density surface using both Matplotlib and Plotly. CITATION.cff CMakeLists.txt CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md CONTRIBUTING.md LICENSE.txt README.md cmake documentation examples mkdocs.yml process process-tracking-data process.egg-info requirements.txt requirements_dev.txt ruff.toml scripts setup.py source tests tracking valgrind-python.supp Add 2nd Generation REBCO critical current density calculations and visualizations - Introduced a new image file for the critical current density surface of 2nd Generation REBCO superconductors. - Updated the superconductors documentation to include a detailed section on 2nd Generation REBCO\, including critical parameters and equations. - Added a new Python script for plotting the critical current density surface at zero strain\, utilizing both Matplotlib and Plotly for visualization. - Enhanced the \`jcrit_rebco\` function in the superconductors module to calculate critical current density with improved parameter validation and documentation. CITATION.cff CMakeLists.txt CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md CONTRIBUTING.md LICENSE.txt README.md cmake documentation examples mkdocs.yml process process-tracking-data process.egg-info requirements.txt requirements_dev.txt ruff.toml scripts setup.py source tests tracking valgrind-python.supp Add Durham REBCO model implementation and documentation - Introduced a new image for the critical current density surface of the Durham REBCO model. - Updated the superconductors documentation to include the Durham REBCO model\, its derivation\, and parameters. - Added a new Python script for plotting the critical current density surface at zero strain using the Durham REBCO model. - Implemented the \`gl_rebco\` function in the superconductors module to calculate critical current density\, critical field\, and critical temperature based on the Durham model. - Enhanced documentation for the \`gl_nbti\` and \`gl_rebco\` functions with references to relevant studies. CITATION.cff CMakeLists.txt CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md CONTRIBUTING.md LICENSE.txt README.md cmake documentation examples mkdocs.yml process process-tracking-data process.egg-info requirements.txt requirements_dev.txt ruff.toml scripts setup.py source tests tracking valgrind-python.supp Add Hazelton-Zhai REBCO model implementation and documentation - Introduced a new model \`hijc_rebco\(\)\` for calculating critical current density based on the Hazelton-Zhai parameterization. - Added a new image \`Hazelton_Zhai_REBCO_zero_strain.png\` depicting the critical current density surface. - Updated \`superconductors.md\` to include detailed documentation of the Hazelton-Zhai model\, including equations and fit parameters. - Created a plotting script \`hazelton_zhai_rebco_critical_surface.py\` to visualize the critical current density surface. - Modified \`pfcoil.py\` and \`superconducting_tf_coil.py\` to utilize the new \`hijc_rebco\(\)\` function with appropriate parameters. - Updated \`superconductors.py\` to enhance the \`hijc_rebco\(\)\` function with additional parameters for tape dimensions. - Adjusted unit tests in \`test_superconductors.py\` to reflect changes in the \`hijc_rebco\(\)\` function signature.
